# Solver Build Policy

When working in this repository, use the following defaults for C++ solver builds.

- Prefer explicit configure/build dirs:
  - `cmake -S solver -B build-solver ...`
- Default build type:
  - `-DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release`
- Default parallelism on shared/remote machines:
  - `cmake --build build-solver -j1`
  - `ctest --test-dir build-solver -j1 --output-on-failure`
- Use higher `-j` only if the user explicitly requests faster build at higher load.
- If changing build commands/docs, keep `CONTRIBUTING.md` aligned with this policy.
- After running build/test commands, report the exact commands used.
